1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>Lady Gaga  - “混乱”（Polydor）</strong></li></ol><p> “ Koko”以座右铭的名字命名，继续以“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-lottery-winners-pensive-new-single-ragdoll-featuring-nickelbacks-chad-kroeger-3847486">Ragdoll</a> ”为特色，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nickelback">Nickelback</a>的Chad Kroeger的来宾露面，乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nickelback-announce-2024-uk-and-european-arena-tour-with-the-lottery-winners-buy-tickets-3549632">在去年的英国和欧洲竞技场巡回赛上支持“您如何让我想起我的摇滚乐手”</a> 。专辑中的其他嘉宾包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">弗兰克·特纳（Frank Turner）</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Shed</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reverend-and-the-makers">Reverend＆The Makers。</a></p><p>该专辑还在官方乙烯基专辑榜上和官方唱片商店榜上首次亮相。彩票获奖者将于下个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-announce-keep-on-keeping-on-2025-uk-tour-tickets-3800813">继续前进英国的头条新闻巡回赛</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/lottery-winners-tickets/artist/2169944?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=xOnTBHWu7xyKRF4SKGSfxVZQUks0aAVlGVH-Tg0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到剩余的门票</a>。此外，乐队将于今年在英国节日巡回演出，定于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-sting-stereophonics-announced-headliners-isle-of-wight-festival-2025-3796064">怀特岛节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendal-calling-2024-line-up-the-prodigy-courteeners-fatboy-slim-kaiser-chiefs-and-more-announced-buy-tickets-3808588">肯德尔召唤</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bearded-theory-adds-paul-heaton-english-teacher-nadine-shah-the-lottery-winners-and-more-to-stacked-2025-line-up-3828411">胡须理论</a>等。</p><p>去年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lottery-winners">彩票冠军的</a>主持人汤姆·瑞兰斯（Thom Rylance） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-interview-kate-nash-row-working-class-arts-koko-album-robbie-williams-3821969">向<em>NME</em>讲述</a>了他对与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kate-nash">凯特·纳什（Kate Nash）</a>连续不缺乏工人阶级代表的遗憾。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lottery-winners-criticise-kate-nashs-attempt-to-represent-the-working-class-musician-due-to-brit-school-education-3817188">Rylance发推文说，纳什不应该试图代表工人阶级的音乐家</a>，并批评她作为英国学校的前学生的背景，而是错误地将其标记为收费机构。</p><p>他向纳什道歉，他说：“对不起，真是。凯特所做的事情很棒，因为她正在强调工人阶级的艺术中的系统性问题。在音乐界和其他艺术中，缺乏工人阶级的人在音乐行业和其他艺术中都非常不成比例。我同意凯特所说的一切，而且我想加入她的声音。”</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-lottery-winners-score-second-number-one-album-with-koko-this-is-for-grassroots-music-this-is-for-the-working-class-3850188">彩票获奖者与“ Koko”获得第二张专辑：“这是为基层音乐。这是为工人阶级的，这是</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现的。</p> ;
