system宣布2025 Hollywood Bowl共同头条节目</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pulps-Jarvis-Cocker-and-LCD-Soundsystems-James-Murphy.-Credit-Sacha-Lecca-and-Michael-Buckner-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="纸浆的Jarvis Cocker和LCD Soundsystem的James Murphy。学分：Sacha Lecca和Michael Buckner通过Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pulps-Jarvis-Cocker-and-LCD-Soundsystems-James-Murphy.-Credit-Sacha-Lecca-and-Michael-Buckner-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pulps-Jarvis-Cocker-and-LCD-Soundsystems-James-Murphy.-Credit-Sacha-Lecca-and-Michael-Buckner-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pulps-Jarvis-Cocker-and-LCD-Soundsystems-James-Murphy.-Credit-Sacha-Lecca-and-Michael-Buckner-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pulps-Jarvis-Cocker-and-LCD-Soundsystems-James-Murphy.-Credit-Sacha-Lecca-and-Michael-Buckner-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pulps-Jarvis-Cocker-and-LCD-Soundsystems-James-Murphy.-Credit-Sacha-Lecca-and-Michael-Buckner-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pulps-Jarvis-Cocker-and-LCD-Soundsystems-James-Murphy.-Credit-Sacha-Lecca-and-Michael-Buckner-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Pulp">PULP</a>和<a href="/artists/LCD-Soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a>宣布了将于今年晚些时候举行的2025个好莱坞碗共同头条节目。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986"><b>LCD Soundsystem Live on Glastonbury 2024：Balearic Bliss for Somerset Sunset</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>今天，两支乐队透露，他们将于9月25日和26日在洛杉矶的好莱坞碗上分享舞台，以在天使之城进行两晚居留。 “您看到了双人……而且还可以。@WelovePulp和@lcdsoundsystem。一起，在2025年9月在@hollywoodbowl @hollywoodbowl共住了两个晚上。这是梦想是由梦想组成的。带上跳舞鞋。#SeeingDuble。”</p><p>贾维斯·科克（Jarvis Cocker）还在他的官方Facebook页面上分享了他对演出的兴奋。 “它必须有一天发生，我们在如此出色的公司中……来吧，活着！”他写道。好莱坞碗的两个晚上是唯一以这张标志性双账单为特色的确认日期。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">您正在看到双人……一切都可以。 <a href="https://twitter.com/welovepulp?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@WelovePulp</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/lcdsoundsystem?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@lcdsoundsystem</a> 。共同在2025年9月在<a href="https://twitter.com/HollywoodBowl?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@hollywoodbowl的@hollywoodbowl</a>在一起。这就是梦想的成就。带上跳鞋。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/seeingdouble?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SeeingDouble</a> <a href="https://t.co/ovsLcmkX26">pic.twitter.com/ovslcmkx26</a></p><p> - 纸浆（@WelovePulp） <a href="https://twitter.com/welovepulp/status/1905666541355466757?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年3月28日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3Dpfbid0yRabPXCeWkhqtSJXcjkwgNfq4XQtRzP1XymSo9gdWvyEE14tevmpbtxUd6fgNiNQl%26id%3D100044304255175&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="738" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>从星期二（4月1日）下午10点至4月3日（4月3日）下午10点开始，将为美国快车持卡人提供票前出售。一名艺术家预售将于周三（4月2日）下午10点在此处提供<a href="https://events.seated.com/lcd-pulp-hollywood-bowl" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>注册的粉丝。艺术家预售将持续到星期四（4月3日）下午10点。</p><p>通用门票销售将于周五（4月4日）下午10点开始。您可以访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fpulp-tickets%2Fartist%2F747247" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。</p><p> This is not the first time the legendary Sheffield band and Brooklyn group have been linked together. Back in 2013, LCD Soundsystem frontman James Murphy <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-35-1259132">produced Pulp&#39;s reunion single &#39;After You&#39;.</a></p><p> The track was first demoed by Cocker and co during the sessions for their 2001 LP &#39;We Love Life&#39;. The version that ended up being released was freshly recorded in November 2012 before being finished off with Murphy in December of that year. &#39;After You&#39; marked Pulp&#39;s first new single in eleven years. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="您先请" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WARGijqaYQM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> In other Pulp news, it was recently announced that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-donate-to-live-trusts-grassroots-venues-fund-with-1-addition-on-uk-arena-tour-tickets-3843605">they will be the first band to contribute to the LIVE Trust</a> , where £1 from every ticket sold <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-announce-summer-2025-uk-arena-tour-you-deserve-more-and-we-have-more-buy-tickets-3838073" target="_blank" rel="noopener">at their summer 2025 UK arena tour</a> will be given to fund financial support to those working across live music.</p><p> The band <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-confirm-2023-reunion-with-details-of-huge-uk-and-ireland-tour-3338431">reunited in 2023 for the first Pulp shows since 2012</a> , and played various new songs while out on the road, such as<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-debut-simmering-new-song-farmers-market-3795488">&#39;Farmer&#39;s Market&#39;</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-debut-new-song-spike-island-as-they-kick-off-us-tour-3792000">&#39;Spike Island&#39;</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-debut-another-brooding-new-song-my-sex-3792774">&#39;My Sex&#39;</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-debut-new-song-youve-got-to-have-love-at-brooklyn-concert-3793684">&#39;You&#39;ve Got To Have Love&#39;</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-debut-new-song-background-noise-live-in-mexico-3542753">&#39;Background Noise&#39;</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-debut-a-sunset-at-flow-festival-watch-footage-setlist-3782859#:~:text=Pulp%20performed%20'A%20Sunset'%20live,at%20Flow%20Festival%20this%20weekend.&amp;text=The%20song%2C%20which%20is%20co,Leadmill%20in%20their%20native%20Sheffield.">&#39;A Sunset&#39;</a> .</p><p> Then, last summer, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-reportedly-back-in-the-studio-after-jarvis-cocker-spotted-in-walthamstow-3783688">it was reported that the group were “back in the studio”</a> after frontman Cocker was spotted in Walthamstow, London. The singer was pictured carrying an orange Rough Trade tote bag while waving at the camera. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDej9jjNzUL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: